'''PSAS-5128''' was a sub-adult school located in the northern area of the [[Jrade District/Legends|Jrade District]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Its principal was [[Havidald Guffin]].

In [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], there was a minor local uproar when two Level Six students were found with [[Death stick/Legends|death sticks]]. Afterwards, the school instituted mandatory body and locker searches.

